<plot>In this first-person spiritual journey, a Cambodian-Canadian travels with his parents to their Asian homeland. When encountering family he has never known and the dark history of the war and genocide that occurred in Cambodia, he begins to identify with and understand the foreign culture with which he has been raised.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?251959</url></doc>
